OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777900265
OL,3,CTrump says the US will 'guide'
OL,4,Cstranded ships from the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe United States will launch an
OL,8,Feffort on Monday to "guide" stranded
OL,9,Fships from the Iran-gripped Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz, President Donald Trump has
OL,11,Fsaid, as two ships reported attacks
OL,12,Faround the strait.
OL,14,FTrump gave few details about how the
OL,15,FUS would help hundreds of vessels and
OL,16,Fsome 20,000 seafarers. Iran quickly
OL,17,Fdenounced the move as a ceasefire
OL,18,Fviolation.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
