PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777900265
OL,3,CTrump says the US will 'guide'
OL,4,Cstranded ships from the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FTrump said in a social media post on
OL,8,FSunday that "neutral and innocent"
OL,9,Fcountries have been affected by the
OL,10,FIran war, and "we have told these
OL,11,FCountries that we will guide their
OL,12,FShips safely out of these restricted
OL,13,FWaterways, so that they can freely and
OL,14,Fably get on with their business".
OL,16,F"Project Freedom" would begin on
OL,17,FMonday morning in the Middle East,
OL,18,FTrump said on Truth Social, adding
OL,19,Fthat his representatives are having
OL,20,Fdiscussions with Iran that could lead
OL,21,Fto something "very positive for all".
