OL,3,CTrump says the US will 'guide'
OL,4,Cstranded ships from the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FUS Central Command said the initiative
OL,8,Fwould involve guided-missile
OL,9,Fdestroyers, more than 100 aircraft and
OL,10,F15,000 service members, but provided
OL,11,Fno details as to how they would be
OL,12,Fdeployed.
OL,14,FIran's effective closure of the
OL,15,Fstrait, imposed after the US and
OL,16,FIsrael launched the war on February
OL,17,F28, has shaken global markets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
