OL,3,CTrump says the US will 'guide'
OL,4,Cstranded ships from the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FTrump spoke hours after Iran said it
OL,8,Fwas reviewing the US response to its
OL,9,Flatest proposal to end the war and
OL,10,Fmade clear these are not nuclear
OL,11,Fnegotiations. The fragile three-week
OL,12,Fceasefire appears to be holding.
OL,14,FCargo ships attacked nearby
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
