PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777900265
OL,3,CTrump says the US will 'guide'
OL,4,Cstranded ships from the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FOn Sunday a cargo ship near the Strait
OL,8,Fof Hormuz said it was attacked by
OL,9,Fmultiple small craft, the British
OL,10,Fmilitary's United Kingdom Maritime
OL,11,FTrade Operations centre reported,
OL,12,Fwhile another ship was hit by "unknown
OL,13,Fprojectiles."
OL,15,FThey were the latest in at least two
OL,16,Fdozen attacks in and around the strait
OL,17,Fsince the Iran war began, and a
OL,18,Freminder of the risks if the new US
OL,19,Feffort goes forward.
OL,21,FNo injuries were reported.
OL,26,@tD@_OUuD@MO]
