OL,3,CTrump says the US will 'guide'
OL,4,Cstranded ships from the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThey were the first reported attacks
OL,8,Fin the area since April 22. Tehran has
OL,9,Feffectively closed the strait by
OL,10,Fattacking and threatening ships, and
OL,11,Fthe threat level in the area remains
OL,12,Fcritical.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
